<!DOCTYPE html>

<html>
<head>

    <title> Feed | About </title>

    <link href="../css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="../css/style.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="../css/navbar.css" rel="stylesheet">

    <link href="font-awesome/css/font-awesome.min.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Montserrat:400,700" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css">
    <link href='https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Kaushan+Script' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css'>
    <link href='https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Droid+Serif:400,700,400italic,700italic' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css'>
    <link href='https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Roboto+Slab:400,100,300,700' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css'>

</head>

<body>

    <nav class = "navbar navbar-default">

        <div class="navbar-header">

            <button type="button" class="navbar-toggle" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#bs-example-navbar-collapse-1">
                <span class="sr-only">Toggle navigation</span>
                <span class="icon-bar"></span>
                <span class="icon-bar"></span>
                <span class="icon-bar"></span>
            </button>
            <div>
                <a class="navbar-brand navbar-brand-fix" href="/">Feed</a> 
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="collapse navbar-collapse " id="bs-example-navbar-collapse-1">

            <ul class="nav navbar-nav navbar-right">
                <li>
                    <a href="/search"> Search </a>
                </li>
                <% if (message =='loggedin') { %>
                <li>   
                    <a href="/newrecipe">Add a New Recipe! </a>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <a href="/profile">My Profile</a>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <a href="/orders"> My Orders</a>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <a href="/logout">Logout </a>
                </li>
                <% } else { %>
                <li>
                    <a href="/signup"> Sign Up </a>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <a href="/login" class="visible-xs"> Login </a>
                </li>
                <li class="dropdown hidden-xs">
                    <a href="" class="dropdown-toggle" data-toggle="dropdown">Login<span class="caret"></span></a>
                    <ul id="login-dp" class="dropdown-menu">
                        <li>
                            <div class="row">
                                <div class="col-md-12">
                                    Login via
                                    <div class="social-buttons text-center">
                                        <a href="/auth/facebook" class="btn btn-fb"><i class="fa fa-facebook"></i> Facebook </a>
                                    </div>
                                    or 
                                    <br>
                                    <form action="/login" method="post" class="form" role="form">
                                        <div class="form-group">
                                            <label class="sr-only">Email</label>
                                            <input type="text" name="email" class="form-control" id="email" placeholder="Email" >
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="form-group">
                                            <label class="sr-only" >Password</label>
                                            <input type="password" name="password" class="form-control" id="password" placeholder="Password" >
                                            <div class="help-block text"><a href="">Forget the password ?</a></div>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="form-group">
                                            <button type="submit"class="btn btn-primary btn-block">Sign in</button>
                                        </div>
                                    </form>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
                <% } %>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <header class="text-center">
        <h1> Welcome to Feed!</h1>
    </header>

    <div class="container">

        <br>
        <p class="text center">
             We all know how much we love homecooking. Feed provides the opportunity to enjoy eating and making food with others. Check out other peoples recipes and try them out for yourself. Order anywhere, anytime and enjoy. First, you need to sign up, so click the sign-up button above and join the community. Once you're a part of the community see what others have to offer, search by cuisine or  category and browse throught the delectable dishes offered. One last thing: BE HUNGRY! hungry to eat what others have to offer, or hungry to provide your delicious dishes to others!
        </p>
    
  </div>

  <script src="/js/jquery.js"></script>
  <script src="/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
<footer class="footer text-center">
    <hr>
    <p class="copyright">Copyright &copy; Feed 2016</p>
</footer>
</body>


</html>